Subject: [PATCH 19/91] drm/i915/gvt: replace magic for cursor ddb size with
 GVT_CURSOR_BLOCKS

the cursor ddb size to hard coded to 8 for local display
virtualization. Replace it with GVT_CURSOR_BLOCKS

